questions.question: Where exactly should the + button be positioned relative to the search input?

options.label: Right of search, before ⌘J kbd
options.description: The + button moves outside the search input but stays before the ⌘J keyboard shortcut indicator

options.label: Right of ⌘J kbd
options.description: The + button moves completely to the right, after the ⌘J keyboard shortcut indicator

options.label: Between search and ⌘J
options.description: The + button sits between the search input and ⌘J, all as separate elements with spacing
